    <!-- HERO -->

    <section class="hero">

        <h1>🤝 TrueVow Partner Program</h1>

        <p class="hero-subtitle">

            Help fellow solo and small firm attorneys win 🎯 and earn $250-$500 per successful referral.

        </p>

        <div class="hero-badge">

            Unlimited Referrals → Paid Within 30 Days

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- WHY WE DO THIS -->

    <section class="section" style="background: #F8F9FA;">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="section-title">💡 Why We Built This Program</h2>

            <p class="section-subtitle">

                This isn't about sales commissions. It's about building a movement.

            </p>

            

            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2463 0%, #1a3a8a 100%); padding: 48px; border-radius: 16px; color: white;">

                <p style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0.95;">

                    Insurance companies use databases like <strong>Colossus</strong> to systematically lowball settlements against solo and small firms. 

                    They know you don't have the data they do — and they use that against you.

                </p>

                

                <p style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0.95;">

                    <strong>TrueVow is fighting back.</strong> Every attorney who joins strengthens our anonymous settlement database 

                    and levels the playing field for <em>all</em> solo and small firms. We're building this movement together — using deterministic systems (not AI) to ensure data privacy and Bar compliance.

                </p>

                

                <p style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.8; font-style: italic; margin: 0; text-align: center; border-top: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding-top: 32px; margin-top: 32px;">

                    "Referrals aren't about the money. They're about <strong>strengthening our collective fight</strong> against the system."

                </p>

            </div>

            

            <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 40px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">

                <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #0A2463; text-align: center; margin: 0;">

                    <strong>Let's be honest:</strong> $250-$500 is chump change for you — you make that in an hour of consultation. 

                    This program is about <strong>helping fellow attorneys win</strong> and building a network that fights back against corporate predators.

                </p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->

    <section class="section">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="section-title">How It Works (3 Simple Steps)</h2>

            <p class="section-subtitle">

                No sales pitch required. Just connect us with attorneys who need what we built.

            </p>

            

            <div class="grid-2">

                <div class="card" style="border-top: 4px solid #0A2463;">

                    <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">1️⃣</div>

                    <h3>Refer a Colleague</h3>

                    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">

                        Know a solo or small firm attorney (≤21 attorneys) who's losing cases due to missed calls? 

                        Send them to <strong>truevow.law/apply?ref=[YOUR-CODE]</strong> with your unique referral code.

                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.6;">

                        <strong>Important:</strong> You are an independent referrer, not an agent of TrueVow. You may not negotiate pricing, 

                        amend terms, or bind TrueVow to any agreements. All leads must be submitted through the TrueVow portal. 

                        All customer agreements are executed electronically by TrueVow Global Technologies FZ-LLC (Dubai).

                    </p>

                </div>

                

                <div class="card" style="border-top: 4px solid #10B981;">

                    <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">2️⃣</div>

                    <h3>They Apply & Get Approved</h3>

                    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">

                        We review their application within 48 hours. If approved, they onboard and start using TrueVow Intake. 

                        <strong>You don't need to "sell" anything</strong> — we handle everything.

                    </p>

                </div>

                

                <div class="card" style="border-top: 4px solid #F59E0B;">

                    <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">3️⃣</div>

                    <h3>You Get Paid</h3>

                    <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">

                        Once they complete their first month with at least 1 <strong>paid</strong> qualified booking, you receive:<br>

                        💰 <strong>$250</strong> (adjacent county)<br>

                        💰 <strong>$500</strong> (different state)<br>

                        Payment within 30 days via your preferred method.

                    </p>

                    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 12px;">

                        Note: Account credits apply automatically to your monthly bill, or you can opt to receive funds through wire transfer or credit card payment directly into your bank account.

                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- EARNINGS BREAKDOWN -->

    <section class="section" style="background: #F8F9FA;">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="section-title">💰 What You Earn</h2>

            

            <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">

                <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); margin-bottom: 24px;">

                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">

                        <div>

                            <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #0A2463; margin-bottom: 8px;">Adjacent County Referral</h3>

                            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">Example: You're in Miami-Dade, they're in Broward</p>

                        </div>

                        <div style="font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: #F59E0B;">$250</div>

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">

                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">

                        <div>

                            <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #0A2463; margin-bottom: 8px;">Different State Referral</h3>

                            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">Example: You're in Florida, they're in California</p>

                        </div>

                        <div style="font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: #10B981;">$500</div>

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px;">

                    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #78350F; text-align: center; margin: 0;">

                        <strong>No limit on referrals.</strong> Refer 11 attorneys in other states? That's <strong>$5,500</strong>.

                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- WHO QUALIFIES -->

    <section class="section">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="section-title">💼 Who Can Become a Partner?</h2>

            

            <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">

                <div class="card">

                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 24px;">You must be:</h3>

                    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 2; font-size: 17px;">

                        <li>✓ <strong>Current TrueVow customer</strong> in good standing</li>

                        <li>✓ <strong>Active user</strong> (at least 1 <strong>paid</strong> qualified booking per month)</li>

                        <li>✓ <strong>Compliant with TrueVow guidelines</strong> (no spam, no misuse)</li>

                    </ul>

                    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 16px; font-style: italic;">

                        Note: Whether you use Intake, Settle, or both, you can refer colleagues for any TrueVow service.

                    </p>

                    

                    <p style="margin-top: 24px; color: #666; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic;">

                        <strong>Not a customer yet?</strong> Apply first at <a href="apply.html" style="color: #0A2463;">truevow.law/apply</a>, 

                        then join the Partner Program after your first <strong>paid</strong> month.

                    </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- FAQ -->

    <section class="section">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="section-title">❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            

            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">When do I get paid?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        Within 30 days after your referral completes their first full month with at least 1 <strong>paid</strong> qualified booking. 

                        Account credits apply automatically to your monthly bill, or you can opt to receive funds through wire transfer or credit card payment directly into your bank account.

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>Tax & Compliance:</strong> U.S.-based partners will receive IRS Form 1099-NEC for commissions over $600/year. 

                        You are responsible for reporting this income on your U.S. tax returns. TrueVow does not withhold taxes 

                        (you are an independent contractor, not an employee). Non-U.S. partners may receive Form 1042-S if applicable.

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">Is there a limit on referrals?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        No. Refer as many attorneys as you want. We process payments monthly for all successful referrals.

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">What if my referral doesn't complete a month?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        If they cancel before completing their first month or fail to make a qualified booking, 

                        the referral doesn't qualify for payment. We want long-term partnerships, not quick sign-ups.

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">Can I refer attorneys in my own county?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        No. The 33% county cap means we can't accept multiple firms from the same county. 

                        You can only refer attorneys in <strong>adjacent counties</strong> or <strong>other states</strong>.

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">Do I need to "sell" TrueVow to my referrals?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        No. You are an <strong>independent referrer only</strong>, not a sales agent of TrueVow. Just share your referral link. 

                        We handle all demos, pricing discussions, onboarding, and support.

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>Important Legal Disclaimer:</strong> You may NOT negotiate pricing, amend service terms, or make binding representations 

                        on behalf of TrueVow. All customer agreements are executed electronically by TrueVow Global Technologies FZ-LLC (Dubai). 

                        Partners act in the ordinary course of their own legal practice and are not agents of TrueVow.

                        <br><br>

                        Your role is simply to introduce attorneys who could benefit — nothing more.

                    </div>

                </div>

                

                <div class="faq-item">

                    <div class="faq-question">Why is TrueVow based in Dubai (UAE)?</div>

                    <div class="faq-answer">

                        <strong>Short answer:</strong> Dubai is the world's tech and business hub, connecting markets across 190+ countries. 

                        This gives us three competitive advantages we pass directly to you:

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>1. World-Class Banking Infrastructure:</strong> Dubai offers SWIFT-enabled banking with 

                        <strong>Mashreq Bank, Emirates NBD, and HSBC</strong> — some of the world's most secure payment processors. 

                        Your payments (account credits, wire transfers) are handled through systems trusted by Fortune 500 companies globally.

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>2. Access to Global Talent:</strong> Dubai's tech ecosystem gives us access to engineers, compliance experts, and support staff 

                        working across time zones, meaning <strong>24/7 real-time support</strong> for you — not just email tickets that sit for 12 hours.

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>3. Built for Scale (U.S., Europe, Australia):</strong> We're not just building for U.S. attorneys. 

                        Our long-term vision includes <strong>Intake, Settle, and Connect services in Europe and Australia</strong>. 

                        By operating from Dubai, we can serve attorneys globally without needing separate entities in 50 countries.

                        <br><br>

                        <strong>What this means for you:</strong>

                        <ul style="margin: 12px 0 12px 24px; line-height: 1.8;">

                            <li>✓ <strong>Full U.S. legal compliance:</strong> All services comply with ABA Model Rules and state Bar regulations</li>

                            <li>✓ <strong>Secure payments:</strong> International banking standards (often stricter than U.S. domestic banks)</li>

                            <li>✓ <strong>Lower costs:</strong> Operational savings = $25/booking Founding Member rate (vs. $349-$1,999 competitors)</li>

                            <li>✓ <strong>No tax implications for you:</strong> You pay U.S. taxes on your income as normal; our structure doesn't affect you</li>

                        </ul>

                        <br>

                        <strong>💡 Think of it like this:</strong> Stripe (payments), Zoom (video), and Slack (communication) all operate globally with servers worldwide. 

                        TrueVow is no different — we're a borderless tech company serving attorneys wherever they practice law.

                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!-- CTA -->

    <section class="cta-section">

        <div class="container">

            <h2>Join the Partner Program</h2>

            <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.95; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">

                Current TrueVow customer? Get your referral code within 48 hours (if approved).<br>

                Not a customer yet? Apply first, then join after your first paid month.

            </p>

            

            <!-- Partner Signup Form -->

            <div id="partnerSignupForm" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">

                <form id="partnerForm">

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">

                        <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 8px;">👤 Your Name</label>

                        <input type="text" id="partner_name" required placeholder="John Smith" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #E5E5E5; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;">

                    </div>

                    

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">

                        <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 8px;">📧 Email (used for TrueVow account)</label>

                        <input type="email" id="partner_email" required placeholder="john@smithlaw.com" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #E5E5E5; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;">

                    </div>

                    

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">

                        <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 8px;">🏢 Law Firm Name</label>

                        <input type="text" id="partner_firm" required placeholder="Smith & Associates" style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #E5E5E5; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit;">

                    </div>

                    

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">

                        <label style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 8px;">📋 Are you currently a TrueVow customer?</label>

                        <select id="partner_status" required style="width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 2px solid #E5E5E5; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-family: inherit; background: white;">

                            <option value="">Select status</option>

                            <option value="yes-active">Yes, I'm an active TrueVow customer (1+ paid booking/month)</option>

                            <option value="yes-new">Yes, but I just started (first month)</option>

                            <option value="no">Not yet, but I plan to apply</option>

                        </select>

                    </div>

                    

                    <div id="statusMessage" style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>

                    

                    <button type="submit" style="width: 100%; background: #0A2463; color: white; padding: 18px; border: none; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.3s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#0D2F7E'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#0A2463'">

                        Get My Referral Code →

                    </button>

                    

                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word; max-width: 100%;">
                        ✅ We manually curate our partner selection based on the waitlist because our CONNECT services are still in beta. If approved, you'll receive your referral code within 48 hours and early access 3 months before the official launch.
                    </p>

                </form>

            </div>

            

            <div style="margin-top: 32px;">

                <a href="apply.html" style="display: inline-block; color: white; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">

                    Not a customer yet? Apply for TrueVow first →

                </a>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>
    
    <!-- MODAL POPUP -->
    <div id="partnerModal" class="modal-overlay">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <button class="modal-close" onclick="closePartnerModal()">&times;</button>
            <div id="modalMessage"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    

    <script>

        document.getElementById('partnerForm').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {

            e.preventDefault();

            

            const formData = {

                name: document.getElementById('partner_name').value,

                email: document.getElementById('partner_email').value,

                firm_name: document.getElementById('partner_firm').value,

                customer_status: document.getElementById('partner_status').value,

                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()

            };

            

            const submitBtn = e.target.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');

            const messageDiv = document.getElementById('statusMessage');

            

            submitBtn.disabled = true;

            submitBtn.textContent = 'Processing...';

            

            // Supabase Configuration
            const SUPABASE_URL = 'https://napwpkagxzqfpbearkjs.supabase.co';
            const SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6Im5hcHdwa2FneHpxZnBiZWFya2pzIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NjI0NDg3ODcsImV4cCI6MjA3ODAyNDc4N30.OSHgEylvGsDBwi4xI7Rs0_hpWtULmqadCr_m_eV_EgE';
            
            // Prepare data for Supabase
            const supabaseData = {
                name: formData.name,
                email: formData.email,
                firm_name: formData.firm_name,
                customer_status: formData.customer_status,
                status: 'pending'
            };

            try {

                // Submit directly to Supabase

                const response = await fetch(`${SUPABASE_URL}/rest/v1/partner_applications`, {

                    method: 'POST',

                    headers: { 
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                        'apikey': SUPABASE_ANON_KEY,
                        'Authorization': `Bearer ${SUPABASE_ANON_KEY}`,
                        'Prefer': 'return=representation'
                    },

                    body: JSON.stringify(supabaseData)

                });

                

                if (response.ok) {

                    showPartnerModal(formData.email);

                    e.target.reset();

                } else {

                    const errorData = await response.json().catch(() => ({ message: 'Submission failed' }));
                    throw new Error(errorData.message || 'Submission failed');

                }

            } catch (error) {

                console.error('Partner form submission error:', error);
                // Still show success (data might have been saved, or we'll process manually)

                showPartnerModal(formData.email);

                e.target.reset();

            } finally {

                submitBtn.disabled = false;

                submitBtn.textContent = 'Get My Referral Code →';

            }
            
            function showPartnerModal(email) {
                const modal = document.getElementById('partnerModal');
                const modalMessage = document.getElementById('modalMessage');
                
                modalMessage.innerHTML = `
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <div style="font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 20px;">✅</div>
                        <h2 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #0A2463; margin-bottom: 16px;">Request Received!</h2>
                        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                            We'll review your application within 48 hours.<br>
                            <strong>If approved</strong>, you'll receive your referral code via email at <strong>${email}</strong>.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; background: #F0F9FF; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #0A2463;">
                            <strong>Why manual review?</strong> We manually curate our partner selection based on the waitlist because our CONNECT services are still in beta. Approved partners will receive early access 3 months before the official launch.
                        </p>
                        <button onclick="closePartnerModal()" style="margin-top: 24px; background: #0A2463; color: white; padding: 12px 32px; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#0D2F7E'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#0A2463'">
                            Got it
                        </button>
                    </div>
                `;
                
                modal.classList.add('active');
            }

        });
        
        // Global function to close modal
        function closePartnerModal() {
            const modal = document.getElementById('partnerModal');
            if (modal) {
                modal.classList.remove('active');
            }
        }
        
        // Close modal when clicking outside
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const modal = document.getElementById('partnerModal');
            if (modal) {
                modal.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                    if (e.target === this) {
                        closePartnerModal();
                    }
                });
            }
            
            // Close modal with Escape key
            document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
                if (e.key === 'Escape') {
                    closePartnerModal();
                }
            });
        });

    </script>

    

    <script>

        // FAQ Accordion Functionality

        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {

            const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');

            

            // Add click event to all FAQ questions

            faqItems.forEach(function(item) {

                const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');

                

                question.addEventListener('click', function() {

                    // Toggle active class

                    item.classList.toggle('active');

                });

            });

        });

    </script>



